{"tha-ap400:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap400:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap400:0.3":"8 Salalamandapiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap400:1.1":"“Nibbute kakusandhamhi, ","tha-ap400:1.2":"brahmanamhi vusimati; ","tha-ap400:1.3":"Gahetva salalam malam, ","tha-ap400:1.4":"mandapam karayim aham. ","tha-ap400:2.1":"Tavatimsagato santo, ","tha-ap400:2.2":"labhami byamhamuttamam; ","tha-ap400:2.3":"Anne devetirocami, ","tha-ap400:2.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap400:3.1":"Diva va yadi va rattim, ","tha-ap400:3.2":"cankamanto thito caham; ","tha-ap400:3.3":"Channo salalapupphehi, ","tha-ap400:3.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap400:4.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","tha-ap400:4.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap400:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap400:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap400:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap400:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap400:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap400:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap400:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap400:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap400:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap400:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap400:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap400:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma salalamandapiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap400:9.1":"Salalamandapiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}